GraphRag Lite

Problem Statement

Given a collection of documents, the system can:

Answer questions
Find related documents/pages
Explain why they are related
Detect likely duplicates vs merely similar content
Traverse relationships across multiple documents

Documents
│
▼
Ingestion
│
▼
Chunking
│
▼
Embeddings
│
├──► Vector Store (FAISS)
│
└──► Relationship Builder
│
▼
Similarity Graph
(NetworkX)
│
▼
Relationship Engine
│
▼
LLM Layer

Datasets:

- arXiv Papers : duplicates are rare but the relationships are natural
- StackOverflow : duplicate detection

Core Features:

1. Question Answering : hybrid serach and symentic search
2. Related pages
3. Relationship Explanation
4. Duplicate Detetctor

Similarities could be due to :

- shared concepts
- same categories
- embedded similarities
